	   <tr><td colspan=2>Greed is the root of ALL evil.&nbsp;&nbsp;The casters that want this only want to sell it and are using the idea of the int/wis on this belt are only using it to get a roll on this.  A fair and wise raid master would never let a caster roll on this unless all the melees already had something better.  And realize all ya idiotic casters out there who think yer the only thing that thinks, hybrids like SKs, Pallies, Rangers, Bards, Shaman, Beastlords, etc. need Haste, Stamina, &amp; either int or wis, so what classes do you think this item is built for? Your idiotic Necro who like to be the tank as well, or your Paladin who tanks AND heals yer ass when yer stupid enough to draw aggro, cause they don't have a fast enough dps to keep up with yer nuking ninny?  If ya wanna die on a raid be my guest and loot this, but if ya wanna live, let yer other broke ass as usual hybrids take this and actually be able to do their jobs properly.<br><br>'Nuff said.<br><br><a href=HTTP://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=338886 target=_new> Renmazuo Skoaldiak of Tallon Zek </a><img src=/ubbnew/graemlins/king.gif> Shadow Knight &lt;4&gt; Bertoxxulous<br>&nbsp;<br>Anbori the Sharing</td></tr>
