	   <tr><td colspan=2>A decent belt, that's for sure.&nbsp;&nbsp;I recently got rid of my Dragonborn sash, even though it have slightly more haste (24 vs 21).  But at my level, I appreciate the fact that it has 10ac 4sta, as opposed to only 2ac (like on the dragonborn).. so in my opinion the great stats compensates for the lesser haste.  Another factor is that not everyone has one, and although that doesn't make a huge difference, it does give me the feeling that my belt is slightly unique, not like everyone else's FBSS.<br><br>As far as haste goes, there are two ways to measure the haste effect.  One, the most common, is the percentage is an INCREASE in overall damage output.  And the other way, is the percentage is removed from the delay (17%).  That's why you have wars going on that FBSS is 17% and 21%.. well both are true, it's just the way you calculate it.<br><br>Considering the rarity, extra stats and WEIGHTLESSNESS, this is an awesome item to have in belt slot.  Worth approx. 15k on Drinal server at this present time.<br>&nbsp;<br>"Power is Found in Unity" - Jorlen of Drinal</td></tr>
